          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Using monocromatic g-rays from neutron  and  deuteron",
                " radiative  capture reactions,  elastic scattering of",
                " photons by U-238 has  been  studied  in  the  energy",
                " range 2 to 10 MeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
